## 📝 配置

环境变量：

```bash
# 火山引擎
VOLCENGINE_API_KEY=your_api_key
VOLCENGINE_ENDPOINT=https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com
VOLCENGINE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id

# API 配置
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
```

